          "text": "In case of welding band (A), cut and remove it."
        },
        {
          "text": "In the case of the low-profile band (B), pinch the band with pliers (C) or similar tool to remove it."
        },
        {
          "text": "In the case of the low-profile band (B), pinch the band with pliers (C) or similar tool to remove it."
