      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "609_3.0_jpn_11035411_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Wrap the vinyl tape (B) from the end of the drive shaft (A) to the spline. Remove the dynamic damper weight from the drive shaft. Remove the vinyl tape."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Be careful not to damage the dynamic damper weight (C)."
      ]
    },
